[normal]. W
[normal]e would like to examine not just the specifics of the cases that we have discussed on previous occasions but where the CQC is on the path of improvement that was acknowledged to be necessary following both of you taking up your roles over the last 12 months. 
[normal]I would like to open by asking you this. It is an acknowledged fact
[normal]—
[normal]and you have both acknowledged it in public many times
[normal]—
[normal]that the CQC, until recently, has not been delivering the service that the public looked to it to deliver. You have both committed the organisation to a process of renewal and raising 
[normal]of 
[normal]standards. The core question I am interested in is
