[normal]David Behan[bold]: 
[normal]The thing that I would emphasise, Andrew, is that, in a legal sense, Parliament has given the CQC as a body the power to inspect and regulate. The 2008 Act sets out our duties and responsibilities and they will be amended by the Bill that is currently in the Lords
[normal],
