[normal],
[normal] and that is the work that we will do as we continue the transformation and change within the organisation
[normal],
[normal] to set out a
[normal]n organisational structure that
[normal] can deliver our purpose with a set of systems and processes 
[normal]that 
[normal]allow us to do that. I do not wish to be boring and bureaucratic about this, but process has its place and we need to make sure it has its proper place in the way that we set up the organisation to move forward.
