[normal]David Behan[bold]: 
[normal]There is no overlap. This is specifically a responsibility we have been asked to take forward in relation to adult social care, not in relation to the NHS. This is as a result of quite a considered consultation by the Department of Health following Southern Cross 
[normal]and its 
