[normal] to put together surveillance metrics which will be about quantity and quality in the way that that market operates
[normal],
[normal] because the 
[normal]relationship between financial resilience and the quality of services was pretty much established in the way that Southern Cross collapsed. So it is possible, I think, for us, as we have done on healthcare, not to be definitive 
[normal]about 
[normal]where failure will take place but to ha
[normal]ve some smoke alarms that cause
